name: Keep Getting Caught Up
description: I almost deleted this one.  But there was something about it that kept drawing me back.  It does not run as smoothly as I thought it should, but then the errors in it remind me so much of life.  We make a plan to live, play and work, but so many times we find ourselves needing to course correct, for all the things we did not know we would encounter, would see, would feel. That is not all bad, sometimes the beautiful things happen in those moments.
